name: Felt wallet "hearts"

name: 5 shapes hanger "seeing rainbow stars"
description:
Absolutely gorgeous hand stitched felt hanging.
5 shapes long, joined with gold ribbons and a black ceramic bead at the end of each length of ribbon. Finished with a sweet little bell.
Beautiful bright colours with contrasting coloured stitching. Stuffed with quality craft stuffing.
These hangings are wonderful in kids rooms, nurseries or play rooms. This one is suitable to add colour all over your home.
Fantastic present for a baby shower, birthday, Christmas or to gift to your own child...perhaps you would like to spoil yourself or a loved one!
